sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UploadStep
    participant API as /api/documents/extract
    participant Pipeline as extraction/pipeline
    participant OCR as ocr/tesseract
    participant Detector as type-detection
    participant Mapper as field-mapper
    participant Flagger as flagger
    participant Store as Zustand Store

    User->>UploadStep: Select file(s) + type hint
    UploadStep->>API: POST FormData {file, documentType}
    API->>Pipeline: extractDocument(file, typeHint)
    Pipeline->>OCR: extractTextFromFile(file)
    OCR-->>Pipeline: OCRResult {fullText, blocks}

    alt typeHint provided and valid
        Pipeline->>Detector: Use typeHint directly
    else no typeHint
        Pipeline->>Detector: detectDocumentType(fullText)
        Detector-->>Pipeline: {detectedType, confidence, reason}
    end

    Pipeline->>Mapper: mapFields(docType, ocrResult)
    Mapper-->>Pipeline: FormLineMap {fields, confidence}

    Pipeline->>Flagger: flagAnomalies(fields, docType)
    Flagger-->>Pipeline: TaxLineItem[] with flagged updates

    Pipeline-->>API: ExtractedDocument
    API-->>UploadStep: JSON {id, type, fields, confidence}
    UploadStep->>Store: addDocument(extracted)
    Store-->>User: Document appears in list
